This video capture adapter features easy-to-use software that will assist you through each step of the conversion process. You will learn how to connect an analog video source and record the video on your computer. It will then guide you on how to watch and share the converted video. You can sync your videos with your iPhone, iPod or Apple TV, giving you several options for sharing videos with your family and friends. This analog video adapter is handy for hobbyists who want to convert home movies.
